###

### Get All Retailers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/retailer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Retailers - Mumbai
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/retailer?city=Mumbai&state=Maharashtra
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Retailers - With Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/retailer?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Retailers - Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/retailer?search=Electronics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Retailer by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/retailer/{{retailerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update Retailer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/retailer/{{retailerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "shopName": "Electronics Plus Premium",
  "ownerName": "Vikram Sethi",
  "mobile": "9988776655",
  "alternateMobile": "9988776654",
  "address": "Shop No. 5, City mall, Level 2",
  "city": "Mumbai",
  "state": "Maharashtra",
  "status": "Active",
  "assignedBdmId": "{{employeeId}}"
}

