###

### Get All Visits
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/visit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Visits - By City
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/visit?city=Mumbai&state=Maharashtra
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Visits - By Date Range
